description: Amundi Global Bioenergy UCITS ETF EUR Acc seeks to replicate, as closely as possible, whether the trend is rising or falling, the performance of the Bloomberg BioEnergy Screened Index (the "Index"), and to minimize the tracking error between the net asset value of the Sub-Fund and the performance of the Index. The anticipated level of tracking error, under normal market conditions, is indicated in the prospectus of the Sub-Fund. For further information, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
